<br>
<br>
And for you people that beleive we support people lie to you.  Well we don't and we all are normally in the same building and record the calls so when you keep calling back ever 5 minutes to ask the same question than yes you are going to get the same answer and eventually someone is going to say you just called about this 5 minutes ago has anything changed since than to update this issue?  If your answer is going to be no than stop calling.<br>
<br>
Yes I know people are not computer savie but if you are going to call in and just tell me it doesn't work at least tell me what doesn't work and it would be wonderful if you could tell me what happens when it doesn't work.<br>
