<br>
Ranting about not being able to find the service tag is silly.  I have been using computers for over 10 years and consider myself fairly proficient in their use but would not know where to find my service tag.<br>
<br>
I am an attorney.  A lot of my time is spent advising clients on how documents work and often times these are answers they could have arrived at themselves if they spent a minute to go through the documents.  However, it is easier for them to simply call their attorney for that answer and that is one of the services we provide.  If they understand the documents better than I do and are able to draft them better, then I am out of a job.<br>
